{
  "id": "adv_event_2502_01_01",
  "title": "サニピ達の\nバレンタイン",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_01-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "私達がチョコレートのTVCMに？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’re going to be in a chocolate TV CM?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 4.3229930878000005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、お菓子メーカーから出演依頼がきたんだ\nサニピに今年のバレンタインを盛り上げてほしいそうだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ we got an appearance request from a confectionery company.\nThey want Sunny Peace to liven up this year’s Valentine’s Day.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.4829933962,
      "endTime": 12.3245354494,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_01-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "CMでは私達の曲を流すんですよね？\nもしかして新曲を作るんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They’ll be playing our song in the CM‚ right?\nDoes that mean we’re making a new song?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.5178687256,
      "endTime": 20.1067228477,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "新曲だけじゃないぞ。お菓子メーカーの\nキャンペーンの一環でイベントも開催する予定だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s not just a new song. As part of the confectionery company’s\ncampaign‚ they’re also planning to hold an event.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.2933894953,
      "endTime": 27.1275162539,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "チョコに付いている応募券を集めて送ると、抽選で\nサニピの限定イベントに招待するという企画だそうだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If people collect and send in the entry tickets that come with to the chocolates‚\nthey’ll be entered into a lottery to be invited to a Sunny Peace exclusive event.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.3275163493,
      "endTime": 34.8525729976,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_01-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "バレンタインのCMに、新曲に、イベントですか\nこれはやらない理由はありませんね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A Valentine’s CM‚ a new song‚ and an event…\nThere’s no reason not to do it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.0392397406,
      "endTime": 42.1747271063,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_01-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "サニーピースのバレンタインイベント……\nどんなステージになるか、楽しみ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sunny Peace’s Valentine event…\nI’m looking forward to what kind of stage it’ll be…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.3880602679,
      "endTime": 48.1463823161,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "全員乗り気みたいだな。なら早速だが\nみんなで相談して決めてほしいことがある。それは――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sounds like everyone’s on board. Then let’s get started—\nthere’s something I want you all to discuss and decide. That is—",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.3397156876,
      "endTime": 56.3988310975,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 57.5354961238
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_01-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "第一回、サニーピースのバレンタインイベント\n企画会議～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The first Sunny Peace Valentine event\nplanning meeting—!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.5854961238,
      "endTime": 64.3161310991,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 64.5027977945
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_01-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "どんどんぱふぱふ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Bom Bom Honk Honk",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.5027977945,
      "endTime": 66.4204168321,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 66.6337501606
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_01-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "という訳で、イベントでどんなことをやるのか\nみんなで話し合って決めるわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So then‚ let’s all talk it out\nand decide what we’ll do at the event.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.6337501606,
      "endTime": 72.42424918009999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 72.6242490848
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_01-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "とりあえず、一つ……やることは決まってる……\nイベントで私達の作った新曲を披露する……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For now… there’s one thing we already know we’ll do…\nWe’ll perform the new song we made at the event…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.6242490848,
      "endTime": 81.0430921634,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 81.2297587157
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_01-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "バレンタインといえば恋愛ソングかしら？\n歌詞は私達が書くのよね。どんな曲になるか楽しみだわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Valentine’s Day means a love song‚ I suppose?\nWe’ll write the lyrics ourselves‚ right? I’m excited to see what kind of song it’ll be.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.2297587157,
      "endTime": 90.9118225814,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 91.1184894007
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_01-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "そうね！　曲作りの詳細は改めて考えるとして\n他にイベントでやりたい企画はあるかしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s right! We’ll go over the details of the song later‚\nbut is there anything else you’d like to do at the event?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.1184894007,
      "endTime": 98.6757454317,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 98.869078517
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_01-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "バレンタインらしい企画かぁ……\nチョコを何個食べられるか、みんなで競争するとか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A Valentine-like idea‚ huh…\nHow about a contest to see who can eat the most chocolates?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.869078517,
      "endTime": 106.2248608352,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 106.4315274637
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_01-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "どうしてバレンタインイベントで\n大食い競争しなきゃいけないのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why would we need to have\na big-eating contest at a Valentine event?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.4315274637,
      "endTime": 111.37223018809999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 111.5722303789
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_01-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "私達で手作りチョコを作って\n会場のお客さんに配る……とか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We could make handmade chocolates ourselves\nand hand them out to the audience… maybe?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.5722303789,
      "endTime": 117.9369824808,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 118.1503157378
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_01-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "そこはお菓子メーカーのチョコを配りなさいよ\nそもそも衛生面的に厳しいかもしれないわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s where we should be handing out the confectionery company’s chocolates.\nBesides‚ it might be difficult from a hygiene standpoint.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.1503157378,
      "endTime": 126.3615176917,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 126.554850777
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_01-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "バレンタインの甘酸っぱい思い出を\n一人ずつ話すなんてどうかしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How about each of you sharing\na sweet-and-sour Valentine memory?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.554850777,
      "endTime": 131.6140117725,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 131.8073449533
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_01-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "エピソードトークですね。悪くないと思いますけど……\nみんなは誰かにチョコをあげた経験はあるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "An episode talk‚ huh. I don’t think it’s a bad idea‚ but…\nHave you all ever given chocolates to someone?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.8073449533,
      "endTime": 140.19559892819998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 140.3889322043
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_01-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "毎年、お父さんとお母さんにチョコをあげてるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Every year‚ I give chocolates to my mom and dad.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.3889322043,
      "endTime": 144.4050772429,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 144.5917439859
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_01-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん当たり前。私も毎年あげてる\n推しのアイドル全員と従姉妹のお姉ちゃんに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ that’s only natural. I give them every year too.\nTo all my favorite idols‚ and to my older cousin.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.5917439859,
      "endTime": 152.8846920412,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 153.0713588795
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_01-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "私もいつもお姉ちゃんにあげてるけど……\n怜ちゃんは？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I always give them to my sister too‚ but…\nWhat about you‚ Rei-chan?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.0713588795,
      "endTime": 158.01487971159997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
