      "text": "問題は誰に書いてもらうかよね。私達のことをよく\n知っていて、恋愛や告白に詳しいプロの人……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The question is who we ask. Someone who knows us well‚\nand is a professional knowledgeable about romance and confessions…",
